dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Samuel Bryant. May I have your name, please?
Hi, my name is Teresa Scott.
Nice to meet you, Teresa. Could you provide me with your policy number?
Certainly. My policy number is five eight six two three four zero.
Thank you, Teresa. For security purposes, could you also confirm your date of birth?
Yes, my date of birth is the twenty-second of May, nineteen seventy-eight.
Great, thank you for confirming. Is there anything specific you would like to inquire about today, Teresa?
I wanted to check the status of my recent claim.
I can assist you with that. Let me look up the information. Thank you for your patience, Teresa.
I have checked your claim status. Everything is in process, and we will update you as soon as there are any developments. Is there anything else I can assist you with today, Teresa?
No, that's all for now. Thank you for your help, Samuel.
You're welcome, Teresa. Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
